Detailed Description

cvmx_sso_reset

Writing a 1 to SSO_RESET[RESET] resets the SSO. After receiving a store to this CSR, the SSO must not be sent any other operations for 2500 coprocessor (SCLK) cycles. Note that the contents of this register are reset along with the rest of the SSO.
